Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.82,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,What will you draw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:16.58,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Within this blank slate of a world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:33.60,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Back when we first found one another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:37.10,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Our destinies had already begun to intertwine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:41.52,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,And yet, the hands of fate began to dastardly flip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:45.11,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Starting our lives anew on a blank sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:50.24,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times we may be reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.41,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,We’ll always find our way back to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:58.20,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Fate can never tear us apart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.00,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,The place where our journey began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:05.42,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,In search of our own little happy ending
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.05,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,I will keep looking until I finally find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:11.47,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,An ending where I’ll always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:14.72,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Sharing our heartfelt laughs and soul-crushing tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.14,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,No matter what the future may have in store for us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.85,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,Even as the wheels of fate start to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:27.28,OP1 - ENG,,0,0,0,,I’ll always be right by your side
